Repeat: wyib, insert needle from behind into the yo space and slip both of the strands that lie above this space (i.e., the one on the left needle and the one beneath it) as one stitch; p3
insert right hand needle from behind into the yo space and purl the 3 loose strands tog (i.e., the 2 on the needle, and the one beneath the needle); k3
wyib, insert needle from behind into the yo space and slip both of the strands that lie above this space (i.e., the one on the left needle and the one beneath it) as one stitch; p3
insert right hand needle from behind into the yo space and purl the 3 loose strands tog (i.e., the 2 on the needle, and the one beneath the needle); k3
